  tagged ion-devel-20030412

2003-04-12 19:06 UTC  tuomov
  * trunk: changeset 438
  Added the flag -std=c99 to options to compile luaextl.c as it needs
  va_copy from C99 and some versions of GCC seem to disable this macro
  otherwise.

