2005-02-15 18:06 UTC  tailor@f281.ttorni.ton.tut.fi
  * Tailorization of trunk
  Import of the upstream sources from the repository
  
   http://tao.uab.es/ion/svn/ion/trunk
  
  as of revision 173
  
